{"tid":1417203,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新和理非手段","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:29:04.000Z","uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed98aac19d6e44208b5c4308b4f7e9e5ab68a448","tid":1417203,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:10:07.000Z","msg":"之前元朗出事每幾日前後有唔少錄音流傳，不分黃藍白黑都有聽過。呢個其實係一個宣傳機會，因為圖片同影片只要preview唔啱口味大家就選擇唔睇唔想信，但係錄音就完全唔同，一定要㩒入去聽先知內容。<br />\n我地可以搵人錄定宣傳聲帶，以勸和哥個條為例子，到最後先帶出意思，無論抗爭定遲下區議會都有用。<br />\n啱聽就幫推唔該"},{"pid":"437ede9ca6e4724437bce4494eca4f17fe6b9192","tid":1417203,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"香港示威者已經好冷靜克制 唔好自己嚇自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79102966d742428b4d335c727d7e4799fc293e8e","tid":1417203,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c989de638775f38f445e5403d37a86ef07a6b94","tid":1417203,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001328_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001328_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=57c35035&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001329_204fd6f27813ec488a814ee7dd366cf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001329_204fd6f27813ec488a814ee7dd366cf7.png&h=a04ae1af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001330_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001330_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=